data.description: Nestled on a quiet street with breathtaking panoramic vistas of the Chocolate Mountains in the premier and highly desirable 55 plus gated community of Four Seasons, sits this lovely, original owners & well-maintained canyon IV plan residence (one of the most sought-after and rarely available floor plan). A private inner landscaped courtyard welcomes you to this spacious and light filled home. Pride of ownership is evident throughout the home originally built in 2008. The generous open floor plan features nearly 2700 sq.ft with timeless upgraded ceramic floors throughout, high ceilings, built-in speakers, an elegant fireplace, a formal dining area, a great separation of the main home three bedrooms as well as a lovely fully detached casita with private bathroom. The gourmet chef's kitchen features cinnamon color wood cabinetry, a center island, a large breakfast bar, tremendous amounts of cabinet space and food prep areas, stainless steel appliances & granite slab countertops & an oversized pantry. Relax in the large primary suite with spa-like bath featuring a soaking tub & stall shower, dual vanities, private water closet & walk-in closet. Additional upgrades include a leased solar system (can be purchased). The back patio area is very private and has phenomenal vistas. A two car garage and a separate laundry room with sink complete this home. Four Seasons is an active lifestyle community with clubhouse, sport courts, fitness center, pools/spas, bocce ball & so much more!
